## v0.10.4: Ingest and Chunk Improvement
- Need to identify author, date, page, etc. for chunks/sources for proper
  citations can be generated from a chunk.
- Chunks track their language and have ability to auto-translate and link
  chunks together.
- Track source type (talk, book, etc.)
- Query pipeline takes language into consideration and so will search
  the other languages in the chunks to include in the search space
- Include Chats in query pipeline. Should they be chunked and embedded?
  - Add Chat "projects" to group chats for focused context. Enable linking
    files and embedding to particular projects.
- Should the server also do a ingest file path scan looking for file that
  need to be updated, and then set a file watcher? That way it can either
  auto-ingest in the background or prompt the user.

